<!-- 	//What's happening in the background 
Spring Boot created a group of dependencies that do work well together
You don't need to pick and choose what you need
Parent pulls configuration (version of jars) that informs maven what jars to pull when you specify a dependency
preset list of possible combination of jars that work well without issues is known as Bill of Materials
you only need to worry about the version of the parent
-->